	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_MALL_EVENT_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Shop 'Til You Drop</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_MALL_EVENT_HELP">
			<Text>The advent of consumer culture poses a difficult question to us, ideologocially. Do we engage with the increased quality of life, of sieze state control?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_MALL_EVENT_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Villages +1 [ICON_FOOD] Food, [ICON_GOLD] Gold, and [ICON_CULTURE] Culture. Towns gain +2.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_MALL_EVENT_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>[ICON_GREAT_MERCHANT] Merchants generate +1 [ICON_GOLD] Gold.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_MALL_EVENT_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Shopping Malls reduce -2 [ICON_RESEARCH] Science. Manufactories gain +4 [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_MALL_EVENT_HELP_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Shopping Malls boost +3 [ICON_CULTURE] Culture. However [ICON_STRENGTH] Crime and [ICON_GOLD] Poverty thresholds increase by 5%.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_MALL_EVENT_HELP_CHOICE_5">
			<Text>Shopping Malls reduce -2 [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism. [ICON_DIPLOMAT] Civil Servants generate +2 [ICON_GOLD] Gold and +2 [ICON_GOLDEN_AGE] Golden Age Points.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_MALL_EVENT_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Our advancement as a nation yields benefits for all. My benevolance manifests!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_MALL_EVENT_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>With a larger internal market in which to sell goods, our Merchants will become yet more profitable!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_MALL_EVENT_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>We have no need of 'innovation'. All our citizens shall have the same 'choice' of goods, leaving our Manufactories free to produce other things...</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_MALL_EVENT_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>People should be free to buy whatever they want! And if they can't afford it? Well that's not very free, is it! Let's give everyone credit cards and then they can keep shopping! HURRAY!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_MALL_EVENT_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_5">
			<Text>National industry for national socialists. Foreign companies are just another vehicle for the international conspiracy against this great and noble people.[NEWLINE]...[NEWLINE]If they're already here? Well confiscate their stuff, of course!</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
